            "title_opacity": 100,
            "cwgp_expertise_card_text": "<p>Our vision is to become the most customer-centric NetSuite Solution Partner in the world. We understand how daunting it can be making the switch to a brand new ERP system and we want to be there for all of our Clients, every step of the way.</p>",
